# 🧠 Predicting Psychological Risk Factors of Longevity

## 📌 Overview

This project explores how psychological and behavioral indicators influence long-term health outcomes. Using statistical analysis and machine learning techniques, the study identifies key factors associated with longevity and mental well-being.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Analyze behavioral survey data
- Identify psychological risk factors
- Build predictive models
- Generate actionable healthcare insights
- Visualize trends using Tableau

---

## 📊 Dataset

Large-scale behavioral health survey dataset containing demographic and psychological variables.

Key Features:

- Stress Levels
- Mood Swings
- Social Weakness
- Family History
- Time Spent Indoors
- Coping Mechanisms

